        <p>Aaaaaand we&rsquo;re back! On Saturday, August 16th, <a href="http://www.lacocinasf.org/">La Cocina</a> will be hosting the 6th Annual Street Food Festival in San Francisco&rsquo;s Mission District with over 80 local vendors to celebrate food entrepreneurs in the Bay. We&rsquo;re still working on all the details for this year&rsquo;s epic festival, but read more below on last year&rsquo;s event and what makes this day so special.</p>

